title: Nowhere in Africa (2001)
description:
Nowhere in Africa (2001) 

A Jewish family in Germany emigrate shortly before the Second World War. They move to Kenya to start running a farm, but not all members of the family come to an arrangement with their new life. Shortly after their departure, things are changing in Germany very quickly, and a turning back seems impossible. So everyone has to arrange themselves with the new life in a new continent.
